Actually, I have seen pets used effectively in Hate, Fear, Kael, CoM, epic mobs, and several other places.  I think the only place I haven't seen a mage pet really work well is in ToV, but then again, I dont think anyone's tried yet.  Yes controlling your pet is hard.  I've played a necro, mage, and beastlord and know this well, but I have also seen a Mage and Necro do some serious damage using thier pets in raid situations.  It really comes down to learning how to overcome the problems of pathing.<P>--------------------<P>Idarae Pyrocaster<BR>Sorceress of Veeshan<BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=85595" TARGET=_blank>Profile</A>
